sentences: His debut album, Fly Away, was recorded in Oregon with Christopher Stevens and released in 2003.
His 2008 album is titled Diego's Diary.
In October 2009, he led a songwriting workshop in Thailand.
Wright also recently released some singles which were custom songs he wrote for his fans.
